text: Office Depot is an American office supply retailer headquartered in Boca Raton. They sell office supplies like computers in the United States. It was founded in 1986. The first Office Depot store opened at the Lakes Mall in Fort Lauderdale in 1986. It has since grew to 1,400 locations in the United States. It was merged with OfficeMax in 2013. ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1986 establishments in the United States Category:Companies based in Florida
